OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784281689
OL,3,CAlbanian man jailed for using fake
OL,4,Cmarriage certificate to work in UK
OL,6,FHe said it had a "detrimental effect
OL,7,Fon society where the immigration
OL,8,Fsystem is undermined by people using
OL,9,Ffalse documents".
OL,11,FLaura Atherton, prosecuting, told the
OL,12,Fcourt Hani had applied in May 2022
OL,13,Fusing a marriage certificate which
OL,14,Fstated he had married a Romanian
OL,15,Fnational, referred to as Ms Duna, in
OL,16,FCyprus in 2019.
OL,18,FShe said: "It transpired the marriage
OL,19,Fcertificate was false."
OL,26,@nD@ROUqD@PO]zD@KOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784281689
OL,3,CAlbanian man jailed for using fake
OL,4,Cmarriage certificate to work in UK
OL,6,FCypriot authorities later told the
OL,7,FHome Office the issue number on the
OL,8,Fcertificate did not match their
OL,9,Frecords.
OL,11,FThe court heard Hani, who appeared by
OL,12,Fvideo-link from prison, obtained
OL,13,Femployment with a painting and
OL,14,Fdecorating business and a real estate
OL,15,Fmanagement company and in the tax year
OL,16,F2025/26 he earned more than #24,000.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784281689
OL,3,CAlbanian man jailed for using fake
OL,4,Cmarriage certificate to work in UK
OL,6,FHe was arrested at his home in
OL,7,FLiverpool in June and when
OL,8,Finterviewed, denied knowing the woman
OL,9,Fhe was allegedly married to and said
OL,10,Fhe was forced to make the application.
OL,12,FHani has previous convictions for
OL,13,Fdriving offences and providing a fake
OL,14,FAlbanian driving licence, the court
OL,15,Fheard.
OL,17,FEiran Reilly, defending, said: "Mr
OL,18,FHani has purchased this false
OL,19,Fcertificate. He is a customer, not an
OL,20,Forganiser."
OL,26,@yD@`OU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
