OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784281689
OL,3,CAlbanian man jailed for using fake
OL,4,Cmarriage certificate to work in UK
OL,6,FHe said Hani had paid taxes and there
OL,7,Fwas no evidence his employers had any
OL,8,Fcomplaint with his work.
OL,10,FHe added: "He wanted to stay in this
OL,11,Fcountry. He wanted to work in this
OL,12,Fcountry for a better life."
OL,14,FHani pleaded guilty at Wirral
OL,15,FMagistrates' Court last month to two
OL,16,Fcounts of fraud by false
OL,17,Frepresentation and one count of
OL,18,Fobtaining leave to enter/remain in UK
OL,19,Fby deceptive means.
OL,26,@rD@KOUtD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
