OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784281689
OL,3,CAlbanian man jailed for using fake
OL,4,Cmarriage certificate to work in UK
OL,6,FMr Reilly said Hani wished to return
OL,7,Fto Albania "as soon as possible".
OL,9,FSentencing him, Judge Swinnerton said:
OL,10,F"You were the purchaser of a fake
OL,11,Fmarriage certificate.
OL,13,F"That was significant planning on your
OL,14,Fpart. You planned to buy that in order
OL,15,Fto get permanent leave to remain.
OL,17,F"You knew you were not genuinely
OL,18,Fmarried to that woman."
OL,20,FHe told Hani he would be deported at
OL,21,Fthe end of his sentence.
OL,26,@oD@LOUoD@`O]rD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOUzD@WO]
